ّرَاثَ/inheritance)","transliteration":"watakulūna","root":"أكل","lemmaId":292},{"id":"89:19:2","ayahNum":19,"wordNum":2,"word":"التراث","meaning":"the inheritance","transliteration":"l-turātha","root":"ورث","lemmaId":null},{"id":"89:19:3","ayahNum":19,"wordNum":3,"word":"أَكْلًا","meaning":"with complete consumption (describes تَأْكُلُونَ)","transliteration":"aklan","root":"أكل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"89:19:4","ayahNum":19,"wordNum":4,"word":"لَّمًّا","meaning":"completely/entirely (with emphasis, as an adverb)","transliteration":"lamman","root":"لمم","lemmaId":null},{"id":"89:20:1","ayahNum":20,"wordNum":1,"word":"وَتُحِبُّونَ","meaning":"and you (all) love deeply (the مَالَ/wealth)","transliteration":"watuḥibbūna","root":"حبب","lemmaId":null},{"id":"89:20:2","ayahNum":20,"wordNum":2,"word":"ٱلْمَالَ","meaning":"the wealth (object of تُحِبُّونَ)","transliteration":"l-māla","root":"مول","lemmaId":null},{"id":"89:20:3","ayahNum":20,"wordNum":3,"word":"حُبًّا","meaning":"a love (object of تُحِبُّونَ/you love)","transliteration":"ḥubban","root":"حبب","lemmaId":null},{"id":"89:20:4","ayahNum":20,"wordNum":4,"word":"جَمًّا","meaning":"abundantly (describes حُبًّا/love)","transliteration":"jamman","root":"جمم","lemmaId":null},{"id":"89:21:1","ayahNum":21,"wordNum":1,"word":"كَلَّآ","meaning":"No indeed! (strongly rejecting what comes in إِذَا دُكَّتِ ٱلْأَرْضُ)","transliteration":"kallā","root":"","lemmaId":3101},{"id":"89:21:2","ayahNum":21,"wordNum":2,"word":"إِذَا","meaning":"when (introducing the future event of the earth being crushed)","transliteration":"idhā","root":"","lemmaId":461},{"id":"89:21:3","ayahNum":21,"wordNum":3,"word":"دُكَّتِ","meaning":"was crushed completely (referring to الأَرْضُ - the earth)","transliteration":"dukkati","root":"دكك","lemmaId":null},{"id":"89:21:4","ayahNum":21,"wordNum":4,"word":"ٱلْأَرْضُ","meaning":"the earth (subject of being crushed in دُكَّتِ)","transliteration":"l-arḍu","root":"أرض","lemmaId":null},{"id":"89:21:5","ayahNum"